Winning numbers drawn in ‘All or Nothing Evening’ game
AUSTIN, Texas (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Texas Lottery’s “All or Nothing Evening” game were:
03-05-08-10-12-13-15-17-18-19-20-24
(three, five, eight, ten, twelve, thirteen, fifteen, seventeen, eighteen, nineteen, twenty, twenty-four)
